data.title: Shaquille O'Neal Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Shaquille O'Neal with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

First name means "little one" in Arabic; middle name means "warrior

" In his early teens, lived on an Army base in Germany where his stepfather was stationed

Debut rap album, Shaq Diesel (1993), went platinum

Received numerous honors as an NBA player, including Rookie of the Year (1993); regular-season MVP (2000); NBA Finals MVP (2001, 2001, 2002)

Has worked as a reserve police officer in Los Angeles and Miami
